ISLAMABAD, July 22 (APP): Foreign Secretary Sohail Mahmood welcomed Spain’s Ambassador-designate to Pakistan José A. de Ory here on Friday.
The Foreign Secretary stressed the importance Pakistan attaches to multi-faceted ties with Spain and underlined its desire to sustain the current momentum and further upgrade Pakistan-Spain cooperation in trade, investments, tourism and people to people contacts, Foreign Office Spokesperson said on twitter.
